                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i2">
                     <note>- The "Golden Gospel" book of Qändaʿro Qǝddus Qirqos church.</note>
                     <note>- The canon tables are missing.</note>
                     <note>- The space left for the rubricated, initial lines of 'On the reliability
                        of the Gospels' is unfilled (<locus target="#5va">5va</locus>).</note>
                     <note>- No opening lines for the Gospel of Mark, the Gospel of Luke and the
                        Gospel of John.</note>
                     <note>- The “tituli” of the Gospel of Matthew are only partly numbered (until
                        “tituli” 15); the “tituli” of the Gospel of Mark and of the Gospel of Luke
                        are not numbered; the numbers of the “tituli” of the Gospel of John are
                        mistaken, after "10" follows 20 up to 29.</note>
                  </msItem>
